.TH AUXFETCH 1 "June 2026" "A/UX Workstation" "Local Commands"
.SH NAME
auxfetch \- neofetch-style system summary for A/UX
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B auxfetch
.SH DESCRIPTION
Prints a themed system summary - host, OS, kernel, hardware, uptime,
memory - beside the A/UX logo, in the style of neofetch.  Reads the
terminal palette; looks best in the synthwave rxvt.
.SH SEE ALSO
auxtop(1), aux(7)
